OL,3,CPolice carrying 'scar tissue' of
OL,4,Causterity, says Met chief in bid for
OL,5,Cmore cash
OL,7,FPolice forces are "up for change" but
OL,8,Fstill carry the "scar tissue" of
OL,9,Fausterity, the Metropolitan Police
OL,10,FCommissioner has said in a plea for
OL,11,Fmore cash from the Treasury.
OL,13,FSir Mark Rowley is one of six senior
OL,14,Fpolice officers who, writing in The
OL,15,FTimes on Wednesday, have publicly
OL,16,Fcalled on the Government to provide
OL,17,F"serious investment" at this month's
OL,18,Fspending review.
