OL,3,CPolice carrying 'scar tissue' of
OL,4,Causterity, says Met chief in bid for
OL,5,Cmore cash
OL,7,FThe officers, including the chiefs of
OL,8,FMerseyside, West Midlands, Greater
OL,9,FManchester and West Yorkshire police
OL,10,Fand the head of the National Police
OL,11,FChiefs Council, argued forces needed
OL,12,Fmore money and more officers to deal
OL,13,Fwith "increasing public demand".
OL,15,FSpeaking to the BBC's Today programme,
OL,16,Fthe Metropolitan Police Commissioner
OL,17,Fsaid that while the Government's
OL,18,Fpledges on law and order were
OL,19,F"balanced and sensible", they were
OL,20,Falso "very, very ambitious".
