OL,3,CPolice carrying 'scar tissue' of
OL,4,Causterity, says Met chief in bid for
OL,5,Cmore cash
OL,7,FHe said: "We're carrying the scar
OL,8,Ftissue of years of austerity cuts, and
OL,9,Fthe effects of that. Forces are much
OL,10,Fsmaller when you compare the
OL,11,Fpopulation they're policing than they
OL,12,Fwere a decade or 15 years ago."
OL,14,FHowever, he insisted that police
OL,15,Fforces were "not just asking for more
OL,16,Fmoney", but wanted "radical reform" as
OL,17,Fwell.
