OL,3,CPolice carrying 'scar tissue' of
OL,4,Causterity, says Met chief in bid for
OL,5,Cmore cash
OL,7,FHe said: "We think there should be
OL,8,Ffewer police organisations across the
OL,9,Fcountry that can be more efficient,
OL,10,Fmore capable. We need a proper
OL,11,Fnational police agency that helps co-
OL,12,Fordinate things.
OL,14,F"So we're up for change, we're up for
OL,15,Fdoing things differently, we're up for
OL,16,Fradically reforming. But it also needs
OL,17,Fmore money, because policing is a
OL,18,Fpeople game."
