OL,4,Causterity, says Met chief in bid for
OL,5,Cmore cash
OL,7,FAs well as increasing demand and new
OL,8,Fonline threats from organised crime,
OL,9,FSir Mark and the other chiefs said the
OL,10,Femergency release of prisoners to
OL,11,Falleviate overcrowding and
OL,12,Frecommendations in the sentencing
OL,13,Freview would put more pressure on
OL,14,Fpolicing.
OL,16,FThe policing settlement in Rachel
OL,17,FReeves' spending review, due on June
OL,18,F11, would directly influence whether
OL,19,Fforces are able to deliver as many
OL,20,Fbegin to "lose officer numbers and
OL,21,Fshrink", they said.
