OL,3,CPolice carrying 'scar tissue' of
OL,4,Causterity, says Met chief in bid for
OL,5,Cmore cash
OL,7,F"A lack of investment will bake in the
OL,8,Fstructural inefficiencies for another
OL,9,Fthree years and will lose a once-in-a-
OL,10,Fgeneration opportunity to reform the
OL,11,Fservice."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Sir Mark along with the
OL,14,Fheads of MI5 and the National Crime
OL,15,FAgency are also reported to have
OL,16,Fwritten to the Ministry of Justice to
OL,17,Fwarn about the impact of releasing
OL,18,Fprisoners early.
