OL,3,CPolice carrying 'scar tissue' of
OL,4,Causterity, says Met chief in bid for
OL,5,Cmore cash
OL,7,FThey argued that, without the
OL,8,F"necessary resources" from the
OL,9,Fspending review, the decision to
OL,10,Frelease more people early could be "of
OL,11,Fnet detriment to public safety".
OL,13,FDuring his Today interview, Sir Mark
OL,14,Fsaid the policy had been enacted
OL,15,Fwithout any assessment of its impact
OL,16,Fon policing.
OL,18,FHe said: "The Government have got a
OL,19,Fdifficult problem to fix.
