OL,7,F"For a very long period, sentencing
OL,8,Fpolicy and prison building policy
OL,9,Faren't aligned, hence overcrowded,
OL,10,Fhence they've got to fix that, but the
OL,11,Fsolution that they've come up with
OL,12,Finvolves many, many more offenders
OL,13,Fbeing dealt with in communities rather
OL,14,Fthan being in prison. That's why
OL,15,Fthey're spending more money on
OL,16,Fprobation.
