OL,4,Causterity, says Met chief in bid for
OL,5,Cmore cash
OL,7,F"They've done no analysis on the
OL,8,Fimpact on policing. No analysis of
OL,9,Fthat whatsoever. So that has been
OL,10,Fsettled without any analysis of the
OL,11,Fimpact on policing, the effect on us."
OL,13,FThe sentencing review released last
OL,14,Fweek recommended measures to tackle
OL,15,Fprison overcrowding.
OL,17,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood has
OL,18,Fagreed to allow some criminals,
OL,19,Fincluding violent and sexual
OL,20,Foffenders, to be released early for
OL,21,Fgood behaviour.
