OL,5,Cmore cash
OL,7,FShe also agreed to scrap short
OL,8,Fsentences of under 12 months and have
OL,9,Fmore criminals serve sentences in the
OL,10,Fcommunity instead.
OL,12,FThe Government has said the changes
OL,13,Fwill ensure prisons do not become
OL,14,Fovercrowded, blaming the previous
OL,15,Fadministration for failing to build
OL,16,Fenough prison places.
